Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.tooluser.creator

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.tooluser.creator
The creator package contains classes that are responsible for creating structures. These structures are created using a Procedure containing all the Steps required to provide the required data for a specific type of structure.

The Creator base class contains a set of Step.Factory objects for common components of structures (e.g. for region selection), but not a full procedure. Subclasses of the creator class will have to define that on their own.
